{"tid":1355780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"徵巴打一齊拆班牛屎佬嘅祠堂","createTime":"2019-07-23T11:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T14:01:19.000Z","uid":245278,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"90c69f2aaa6882cdeb4e2f64e07291c5f92f757c","tid":1355780,"uid":245278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:09:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【唔好去搞人地祠堂啊！！！】</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n有人傳緊28號要拆人祠堂<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">千祈唔好做！！！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n搞人祠堂真係唔關事嘅都會變臉見紅，要同鄉黑說不都唔好玩呢d唔該哂。<br />\n<br />\n有朋友喺fb開左po討論<br />\n整合左少少意見想比大家睇<br />\n希望想血債血償既朋友冷靜少少，要搞都唔係應該搞呢種地方🙇&zwj;♀️<br />\n<br />\n第一點，亦都係最重要既係<br />\n我地都好憎警黑兩邊都會做既一樣野，就係&ldquo;無差別打人&rdquo;<br />\n但搞祠堂其實同佢地無差別攻擊為打而打係冇分別架！！！！！<br />\n搞我地既都唔係祠堂點解我地要搞！！！<br />\n認清目標唔好傷及無辜，如果唔係我地就同班渣滓冇分別架喇🙇&zwj;♀️<br />\n<br />\n第二點，其實本身都有好多圍村既人出黎遊行，有年輕人亦有老一輩。<br />\n而家其實都有大把上左年紀撐緊我地嘅人，睇下之前銀髮族既遊行都知。而佢地喺呢啲傳統上都依舊比較保守，接受唔到拆人祠堂咁嘅事。無謂咁樣黎踐踏佢地重要既象徵黎激到佢地唔再支持/俾其他同鄉非議，導致失民意🙇&zwj;♀️<br />\n同埋入村係有可能被指擅闖私人地方，有位俾黑警（選擇性）揸正黎做，我地都唔想再有手足俾黑警食。<br />\n<br />\n拆祠堂只會變香港人打香港人，政府唔會痛。<br />\n我地抗爭重點係7大訴求，拆祠堂係完全冇幫助。只會變洩憤，坐實暴徒之位。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家三思！！！！！！！！！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n文宣圖朋友整緊，但事態緊急喺度呼籲左先！！！！！"},{"pid":"5b3f95d76f113486f475974f56e9e1dd7682ec2b","tid":1355780,"uid":24944,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"唔可以中政府計。<br />\n繼續五大訴求"},{"pid":"a16ada0e7f1431a80b810bdb6ba68766b945ee2a","tid":1355780,"uid":75815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:13:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">負評,上一頁</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6352832c0c816c278335f9cf4fe3e583937a01a6","tid":1355780,"uid":245278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:22:12.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85b8b6dd78202d32f051f0157fee6fb1fb1b52c","tid":1355780,"uid":21255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"有白衫都幫我地發洩左<br />\n就唔好再失焦啦P牌仔"},{"pid":"35838fd6967460af5a51e2d9592a29dd82fad27f","tid":1355780,"uid":245278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:28:25.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc365dfe014a77bf2e48482f8db167e4eae2974","tid":1355780,"uid":245278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a85b8b6dd78202d32f051f0157fee6fb1fb1b52c","tid":1355780,"uid":21255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:28:18.000Z","msg":"有白衫都幫我地發洩左<br />\n就唔好再失焦啦P牌仔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:29:19.000Z","msg":"唔該睇清楚我講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b702824668a902c49ba670e186edd10affdf6b0","tid":1355780,"uid":245278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:35:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該大家睇哂佢啦唔好只睇標題啦乖，唔係好長姐"},{"pid":"80f3a912e1c1e93e7ad2db071ec9ed7acb367f89","tid":1355780,"uid":139931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:36:22.000Z","msg":"又唔好呀?第幾個唔好既POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acaeb91b420f194d357157749245135fee9b059b","tid":1355780,"uid":245278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80f3a912e1c1e93e7ad2db071ec9ed7acb367f89","tid":1355780,"uid":139931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:36:22.000Z","msg":"又唔好呀?第幾個唔好既POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:38:32.000Z","msg":"家下唔係叫人乜都唔